Class Character

  • java.lang.Object
    • harkadventurer.model.Character
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Targetable, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NonPlayerCharacter, PlayerCharacter

    public abstract class Character
extends java.lang.Object
implements Targetable, java.io.Serializable
    Character-type objects store a character's name, maximum health, current health and list of abilities.
    Since:
    09/10/2017

        inMax - The character's maximum hit points
        inAbility - A list of the character's abilities

      • setCurHealth

        public void setCurHealth(int inCur)
        Sets the character's current health. If the input is higher than the character's maximum health, current health will be set to maximum health. If the input is 0 or less, the character's observers will be notified that they have died.
        Parameters:
        inCur - The desired curren health

      • changeHealth
